<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <% content_for(:head) do
      raw(@order.performance.production.conversion_pixel_code) unless @order.performance.production.conversion_pixel_code.blank?
    end %>
    <p>
      Thanks!  Your ticket reservation has been
      <%- member_payments = @order.membership_payments
          if member_payments.size > 0 %>
         made with your <%= member_payments.first.membership.membership_offer.name %>.
      <%- elsif (@order.total > 0) && (@order.paid_with_currency?) %>
          made and your credit card has been charged <%= number_to_currency( @order.total) %> for those tickets.  If you've made a donation, look for a separate email with our thanks.
      <%- elsif @order.paid_with_flexpass? %>
          made and your FlexPass has <%= pluralize(@order.paid_with_flexpass.uses_remaining,'ticket') %> remaining.
      <%- else %>
          made.  You were not charged any money for this order.
      <%- end %>
      Your order id is #<%= @order.id %>, and your tickets will be available for pickup under your name at our box office at 1229 W Belmont ninety minutes before curtain. A confirmation email will be sent shortly.
    </p>
    <p>
      We will see you at the show on <%= @order.performance.performance_date.to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %> at
      <%= @order.performance.performance_time.to_formatted_s(:hour_min) %>. Seating is general admission. If you have any questions, please
      don't hesitate to call us at 773-975-8150 or email us at <a href="mailto:boxoffice@theaterwit.org">boxoffice@theaterwit.org</a>.  Thanks for your support and we'll see
      you at the theatre.  Enjoy the show!
    </p>

  </div>
</div>